Class Red_Black_Tree<Key_Type,Value_Type>

  • java.lang.Object
    • data_structures.Red_Black_Tree<Key_Type,Value_Type>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Set<Key_Type,Value_Type>

    public class Red_Black_Tree<Key_Type,Value_Type>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Set<Key_Type,Value_Type>
    Red Black Tree data structure. Red Black Tree implements Set interface. All values in Red Black Tree are stored with key and value like in a map. User must provide a comparator for key types.
